originalText.text: Zara rules in the life coach world. She is no joke. Working wit Zara quickly got me through a bumble of issues that had plagued me for many years. She is smart, intuitive and nonjudgmental. Zara's only concern is for her clients to reach their personal goals and to have continued success in the future. She will guide you, however ultimately  it is you who is accountable for achieving your personal goals. I highly recommend Zara as a life coach. It was an honor to have worked with her.

originalText.text: I have had the fortunate opportunity to work with Zara for almost a year. During this time she helped me reflect on negative habits and thoughts. Her insights allowed me be more at peace and measured. She has taught me true self care. Since our working together I am healthier physically and mentally, my business has grown and I have a consistent self awareness. If you are ready to be truly self reflective and honest with yourself Zara will guide you to make this leap. Be ready to do the work, she will hold you accountable for the things you want .

Zara is a great life coach, both professional and personable. Her advice is profound and versatile. She applies her own techniques in helping you find the answers to your own questions; is knowledgeable and extensively experienced in life. She gladly shares her experience to help you reilize what you ought to do about yourself and your situation you might be struggling with.
I recommend Zara as a life coach.
